---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SchemaMarkup from "../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro";
import Icon from "../../components/Icon.astro";

// Make this page dynamic via SSR
export const prerender = false;

const publishDate = new Date("May 18 2026");
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "5 min read";

const isPublished = new Date().getTime() >= publishDate.getTime();

---

<BaseLayout
  title="How to Maintain a Clean Home With Pets"
  description={isPublished ? "Pet hair, dander & odors don't stand a chance. Expert tips for keeping your Huntsville, Nashville or Shoals home clean with dogs and cats in the house." : "Coming Soon: How to Maintain a Clean Home with Pets in the House"}
  noindex={!isPublished}
  ogImage="https://thevalleycleanteam.com/og-image.png"
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="How to Maintain a Clean Home with Pets in the House"
    description="Struggling with pet hair and odors? Discover professional tips for maintaining a clean, fresh-smelling home even with multiple dogs and cats."
    publishDate="May 18 2026"
    author={author}
  />
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#FFA985]/20 text-[#FFA985] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Pain Point
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          How to Maintain a Clean Home with Pets in the House
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          {isPublished ? "Expert Cleaning Guide" : "Coming May 18 2026."}
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>May 18 2026</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content Toggle based on Published Date -->
  {isPublished ? (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <!-- DIRECT ANSWER BLOCK - Critical for AEO -->
        <div
          class="bg-[#FFA985]/10 border-l-4 border-[#FFA985] p-6 mb-8 rounded-r-lg"
        >
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 font-medium mb-0">
            <strong>Quick Answer:</strong> Maintaining a clean home with pets is
            entirely possible with the right approach. By building systematic
            cleaning routines and using pet-friendly products, you can enjoy a
            spotless living space without compromising on the joys of pet
            ownership. The keys are managing hair and dander, staying ahead of
            odors, and cleaning consistently.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          How Can You Maintain a Clean Home with Pets in the House?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Pets bring unparalleled joy and companionship, but they also introduce
          unique cleaning challenges. From shedding fur to the occasional
          accident, keeping your home pristine can feel daunting. With a tailored
          cleaning strategy, however, you can overcome these obstacles
          effectively and enjoy a fresh home year-round.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          How Do You Manage Pet Hair and Dander?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Pet hair and dander accumulate quickly, affecting both cleanliness and
          air quality. Where seasonal changes worsen shedding, it's vital to stay
          proactive. Here are some steps to manage pet hair:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600 list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
          <li>Brush pets regularly to reduce shedding.</li>
          <li>Invest in a high-quality vacuum designed for pet hair.</li>
          <li>Use lint rollers or rubber gloves for quick furniture clean-ups.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Odors can linger if they aren't addressed promptly. To keep your home
          smelling fresh, consider these tips:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600 list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
          <li>Clean pet bedding frequently using pet-safe detergents.</li>
          <li>Use air purifiers to improve air quality.</li>
          <li>Regularly clean litter boxes or pet cages to prevent odors.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          What Does a Pet-Friendly Cleaning Routine Look Like?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Developing a routine tailored to your pets' activities is crucial, and
          consistency is the key to maintaining a clean home environment. A simple
          <a href="/services/regular-cleaning" class="text-[#FFA985] hover:underline"
            >regular cleaning routine</a
          > breaks the work into manageable daily and weekly tasks.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Daily Cleaning Tasks</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600 list-disc pl-6 mb-0">
              <li>Wipe paws after outdoor activities to prevent dirt from spreading.</li>
              <li>Sweep or vacuum high-traffic areas daily to tackle loose hair and debris.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Weekly Deep Cleaning</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600 list-disc pl-6 mb-0">
              <li>Wash pet toys and bowls to limit bacteria buildup.</li>
              <li>Mop floors using pet-safe cleaners to remove deeper grime.</li>
              <li>Dust surfaces to capture dander and allergens.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          Which Pet-Safe Cleaning Products Should You Use?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Choosing the right products is essential to keep your furry friends safe.
          Look for non-toxic, enzymatic cleaners that break down stains and odors
          effectively. If you prefer a fully eco-conscious approach, our
          <a href="/services/green-cleaning" class="text-[#FFA985] hover:underline"
            >green cleaning service</a
          > uses non-toxic products that are gentle on pets and family alike.
          Recommended product types include:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600 list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
          <li>Enzymatic cleaners for pet stains on carpets and upholstery.</li>
          <li>Natural, fragrance-free cleaning solutions for surfaces.</li>
          <li>Pet-friendly disinfectants for high-touch areas.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          Why Choose Professional Cleaning Services?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Sometimes maintaining the level of cleanliness you want is challenging
          amid a busy schedule. That's where professional cleaning services like
          The Valley Clean Team come in.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Our trained cleaning specialists follow military-precision standard
          operating procedures to keep your home a healthy environment for both you
          and your pets. With transparent pricing and a 100% satisfaction
          guarantee, you can focus on what matters most—enjoying quality time with
          your pets.
        </p>

        <!-- CLOSING CTA -->
        <div class="bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-xl text-center mt-12">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Reclaim Your Time—Book a Guaranteed Clean Today
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
            Stop worrying about the mess and let us handle the details. Get a free
            quote and see availability—no obligation.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a
              href="tel:2568261100"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition"
            >
              <Icon name="phone" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />Call 256-826-1100
            </a>
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white border-2 border-white rounded-full hover:bg-white/10 transition"
            >
              Request Quote Online
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  ) : (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-gray-100 shadow-inner">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-16 h-16 text-[#FFA985] mx-auto mb-6" />
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-0">Article Coming Soon!</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 m-0">This article is locked and scheduled to automatically publish on <br/><strong class="text-gray-800 text-xl">May 18 2026</strong>.<br/>Check back then!</p>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition shadow-md no-underline">
              Back to Blog
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  )}
</BaseLayout>
